-- Vishal Retail Lenders May Approve Future Group's Debt Plan, Times Reports
-- Thomas Abraham
-- 2010-07-27T01:24:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/vishal-retail-lenders-may-approve-future-group-s-debt-plan-times-reports.html

          
          
             Lenders to India’s Vishal Retail
Ltd. may support a debt recast proposal from Future Group,
disregarding an offer from private equity investor TPG Capital,
the Economic Times reported, citing people it didn’t identify.  
